title: It’s a tie! Farhan Akhtar-Shraddha Kapoor’s Rock On 2 and Tusshar Kapoor’s Kyaa Kool Hain Hum 3 voted as worst sequels of 2016
text: Farhan Akhtar It's a tie! Farhan… It’s a tie! Farhan Akhtar-Shraddha Kapoor’s Rock On 2 and Tusshar Kapoor’s Kyaa Kool Hain Hum 3 voted as worst sequels of 2016 BollywoodLife conducted a poll asking its readers as to which was the worst sequel of 2016. And its surprising to see the poll that consisted of as many as nine films have received almost similar percent of votes from the fans. By Gaurang Chauhan | Updated: February 11, 2017 10:08 am
